```suggestion

```

```suggestion
    (H : âˆ€ x âˆˆ s, P x) (isClosed : IsClosed { x | P x }) (x) : P x :=
  (hs.closure_eq.symm.subset.trans (isClosed.closure_subset_iff.mpr H)) trivial
```

As this can be used as
```
  induction x using hs.induction with
  | H x hx => sorry
  | isClosed => sorry
```
it maybe makes sense to rename `H` to `mem`. Please make sure the PR description is in sync with whatever you decide.
